          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "In the landscape of conversational AI, Chatterbox emerges as a powerful model designed for seamless API integration. This guide offers non-fluffy, actionable advice for experienced API teams to harness Chatterbox effectively in production settings."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "h2",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Understanding Chatterbox Architecture"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "p",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Chatterbox is built on a transformer-based architecture optimized for low-latency responses. Key components include a tokenizer, inference engine, and context manager. For API teams, focus on how it handles concurrent requests and state management. Ensure your infrastructure supports WebSocket or HTTP/2 for efficient communication."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "h2",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Integrating Chatterbox with Your API"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "p",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Start by setting up a RESTful endpoint that proxies requests to Chatterbox. Use authentication tokens and rate limiting to secure access. Example in Python with FastAPI:"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "code_block",
        "lang": "python",
        "value": "from fastapi import FastAPI, HTTPException\nimport requests\n\napp = FastAPI()\nCHATTERBOX_URL = \"http://chatterbox-service:8000/generate\"\n\n@app.post(\"/chat\")\nasync def chat_endpoint(prompt: str):\n    try:\n        response = requests.post(CHATTERBOX_URL, json={\"prompt\": prompt})\n        return response.json()\n    except Exception as e:\n        raise HTTPException(status_code=500, detail=str(e))",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "code_line",
            "children": [
              {
                "text": "from fastapi import FastAPI, HTTPException"
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "code_line",
            "children": [
              {
                "text": "import requests"
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "code_line",
            "children": [
              {
                "text": ""
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "code_line",
            "children": [
              {
                "text": "app = FastAPI()"
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "code_line",
            "children": [
              {
                "text": "CHATTERBOX_URL = \"http://chatterbox-service:8000/generate\""
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "code_line",
            "children": [
              {
                "text": ""
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "code_line",
            "children": [
              {
                "text": "@app.post(\"/chat\")"
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "code_line",
            "children": [
              {
                "text": "async def chat_endpoint(prompt: str):"
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "code_line",
            "children": [
              {
                "text": "    try:"
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "code_line",
            "children": [
              {
                "text": "        response = requests.post(CHATTERBOX_URL, json={\"prompt\": prompt})"
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "code_line",
            "children": [
              {
                "text": "        return response.json()"
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "code_line",
            "children": [
              {
                "text": "    except Exception as e:"
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "code_line",
            "children": [
              {
                "text": "        raise HTTPException(status_code=500, detail=str(e))"
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
