            "text": "Best Practices for Production Deployment"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "p",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Implement health checks and logging for Chatterbox instances. Use containerization with Docker and orchestrate via Kubernetes for scalability. Regularly update the model to incorporate improvements, and establish fallback mechanisms to maintain service during outages. Avoid over-provisioning by analyzing usage patterns with tools like Prometheus."
